text: Juan Carlos Candisano (born 19 April 1966) is an Argentine equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Argentina Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
